            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "I was digging through the code to see if I could fix this myself and do a PR and it seems to already exist! (using `*` instead of `_` but I don't care about that). A little more searching and I found it in the docs as well at https://cython.readthedocs.io/en/latest/src/userguide/external_C_code.html#including-verbatim-c-code\r\n\r\nSo this issue has become:\r\n- you should close #556 and this issue.",
